name: Hamilton
absentee_method: Released as a separate subtotal as first report of the night
nyt_race_description_race: Representative Steve Chabot, a Republican from Cincinnati, is facing one of the biggest challenges of his political career against the Democratic challenger, Kate Schroder, a health industry executive.
poll_display_race: Polls close at 7:30 p.m. Eastern time.
expectations_text_race: Postmarked ballots have until Nov. 13 to arrive, but no additional results will be reported reported for at least a week and a half after the election.
